All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Blog
Represents the main control logic of the Blog application.
BlogException
Custom exception class for handling blog-related exceptions.
FileHandler
Handles file operations, including saving content to a file and reading content from a file.
Input
Handles user input for the blog application.
Lab1
The Lab1 class represents the main class of the application.
Output
The Output class provides methods for displaying information in the console related to the Blog application.
Post
Represents a blog post with title, content, and author information.
Posts
Manages a list of posts, allowing for adding new posts, getting a list of posts, and setting the list of posts.
User
 
Users
Represents a collection of users with methods to manipulate user data.
